{"tid":1727131,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［入黎匯報］黎明行動：中間派/淺黃觀感報告","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:02:29.000Z","uid":282490,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47cbddf9deed0cda55048d1c991afc6a903cd641","tid":1727131,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"而家出一百幾十個果啲十9藍絲，大家就驚輸民意,士氣大跌<br />\n<br />\n唔該搵人𢑥報下<strong>被動罷工&amp;被迫home Office </strong>嘅政治冷感人士點睇<br />\n<br />\n今日返工特登同啲客傾多啲計，我先：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">客仔A：</span></strong> 條腰今個星期無痛過好開心丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西灣河個細路好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（home office 唔駛坐公司張十9櫈,早排親口講過而家社會好亂我邊一邊都唔想撐）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>客仔B: </strong></span>police半夜巡黎巡去，嘈到我訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（比狗嘈到失眠然後頭痛）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>客仔C</strong></span>:返工返左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過好彩放工唔塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b930e3698423910a275161a063e53c07700d9549","tid":1727131,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"二樓係一個索引，有𢑥報大家可以覆呢度 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁新黎嘅讀者會易啲搵返啲報告 唔駛比啲推遮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f0d3bcb951cfa0b489bc6fbe36f2bb9901e3ba","tid":1727131,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96a44286d2d489e297fe182a896ae56bee9ea026","tid":1727131,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"38f0d3bcb951cfa0b489bc6fbe36f2bb9901e3ba","tid":1727131,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"我周圍啲朋友都好